Video_Title: How to Use an Electronic Cigarette: ESSENTIAL Information for New ECigarette Users
Description:
also see - the ultimate beginners guide to electronic cigarettes: http://www.ecigarettedirect.co.uk/ashtray-blog/2013/08/beginners-guide-to-electronic-cigarettes.html

researchers at the recent ecigarettesummit in london explained that new users to electronic cigarettes get less out of electronic cigarettes than experienced users. 

after years of using ecigs, and talking to other users (both new and experienced) we think we know the reason - it's simply the way users inhale when they first switch from a tobacco cigarette to an electronic cigarette. 

fortunately, it's a simple thing to put right, and in this video tutorial tom from ecigarettedirect, the smoker's angel, demonstrates what new users are doing wrong - and how to vape e-cigarettes correctly. 

watch the video to find out - and let me know if you find it useful!

please note, this is only a basic video tip. in a recent blog post, the ultimate guide to electronic cigarettes, you'll find a lot more information on both cigalike and refillable electronic cigarettes. 

in the guide we cover: 

- health issues
- glossary
- how ecigs work
- how to avoid e-cigarette scams
- types of ecigarettes
- how to use different types of ecigarettes

and much, much more. 

check it out here: http://www.ecigarettedirect.co.uk/ashtray-blog/2013/08/beginners-guide-to-electronic-cigarettes.html
